N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4001.4 - Names on daily racing program

State Regulations

The names of the commission members and the
commission's specified employees with their titles, if any, and the address of
the commission's offices shall appear on the daily racing
programs. Notes
